  <class_name>ResidentialHotTubHeaterElec</class_name>
  <display_name>Set Residential Hot Tub Electric Heater</display_name>
  <description>Adds (or replaces) a residential hot tub heater with the specified efficiency and schedule. The hot tub is assumed to be outdoors. For multifamily buildings, the hot tub heater is set for all units of the building.</description>
  <modeler_description>Since there is no Hot Tub Heater object in OpenStudio/EnergyPlus, we look for an ElectricEquipment or GasEquipment object with the name that denotes it is a residential hot tub heater. If one is found, it is replaced with the specified properties. Otherwise, a new such object is added to the model. Note: This measure requires the number of bedrooms/bathrooms to have already been assigned.</modeler_description>
